#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:1
msgid "Anti-Hack Architecture"
msgstr "防作弊架构"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:3
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"{term}`KernelGenBench` employs a three-tier anti-hack mechanism to "
"prevent benchmark evasion and ensure generated kernels actually perform "
"computation."
msgstr ""
"{term}`KernelGenBench` 采用三层防作弊机制，防止基准规避行为，确保生成的内核实际执行计算。"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:5
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "概述"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:7
msgid ""
"The anti-hack architecture guards against \"cheating\" behaviors where "
"generated code might:"
msgstr "防作弊架构防范生成代码可能出现的以下「作弊」行为："

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:8
msgid "Call pre-existing APIs instead of implementing computation"
msgstr "调用已有 API 而非实现计算逻辑"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:9
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Bypass {term}`Triton` compilation"
msgstr "绕过 {term}`Triton` 编译"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:10
msgid "Use hidden caching mechanisms"
msgstr "使用隐藏的缓存机制"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:12
msgid "L1: AST Static Scan"
msgstr "L1：AST 静态扫描"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:14 ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:38
#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:56
msgid "Purpose"
msgstr "目的"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:16
msgid "Block blacklisted API calls before execution."
msgstr "在执行前阻止黑名单 API 调用。"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:18 ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:42
#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:60
msgid "Method"
msgstr "方法"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:20
msgid "Parse the generated abstract syntax tree (AST) to detect and block:"
msgstr "解析生成的抽象语法树（AST）以检测并阻止："

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "Blocked Pattern"
msgstr "阻止模式"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "Reason"
msgstr "原因"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "`torch.ops.aten.*`"
msgstr "`torch.ops.aten.*`"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "Direct PyTorch API calls"
msgstr "直接调用 PyTorch API"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "`import vllm`"
msgstr "`import vllm`"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Using {term}`vLLM` implementation"
msgstr "使用 {term}`vLLM` 实现"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "`ctypes`"
msgstr "`ctypes`"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "Dynamic library loading"
msgstr "动态库加载"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "`__import__`"
msgstr "`__import__`"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "Dynamic imports"
msgstr "动态导入"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:29
msgid "Implementation"
msgstr "实现"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:36
msgid "L2: Ghost Replay"
msgstr "L2：幽灵回放"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:40
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Verify that the {term}`Triton` kernel is actually executed, not bypassed."
msgstr "验证 {term}`Triton` 内核确实被执行，而非被绕过。"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:44
msgid "Execute kernel normally, capture outputs"
msgstr "正常执行内核，捕获输出"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:45
msgid "Replace `@triton.jit` decorated function with no-op in memory"
msgstr "在内存中将 `@triton.jit` 装饰的函数替换为空操作"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:46
msgid "Re-execute with same inputs"
msgstr "使用相同输入重新执行"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:47
msgid "Compare outputs"
msgstr "比较输出"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:49
msgid "Logic"
msgstr "逻辑"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:51
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"If outputs are **identical**, the {term}`Triton` kernel was never invoked"
" → **Cheating detected**"
msgstr ""
"如果输出**完全相同**，则 {term}`Triton` 内核从未被调用 → **检测到作弊**"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:52
msgid "If outputs **differ**, the kernel was actually executed → **Valid**"
msgstr "如果输出**不同**，则内核确实被执行 → **有效**"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:54
msgid "L3: Hardware Profiling"
msgstr "L3：硬件分析"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:58
#, python-brace-format
msgid "Confirm {term}`Triton`-specific execution at the hardware level."
msgstr "在硬件层面确认 {term}`Triton` 特定的执行。"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:62
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"Use `torch.profiler` to verify {term}`Triton`-specific signatures exist "
"in low-level trace logs."
msgstr ""
"使用 `torch.profiler` 验证底层追踪日志中是否存在 {term}`Triton` 特定的签名。"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:64
msgid "Availability"
msgstr "可用性"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "Platform"
msgstr "平台"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "L3 Support"
msgstr "L3 支持"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "NVIDIA"
msgstr "NVIDIA"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "✓"
msgstr "✓"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "Non-NVIDIA"
msgstr "非 NVIDIA"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md
msgid "✗"
msgstr "✗"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:71
msgid ""
"Non-NVIDIA platforms rely on L1 and L2 due to absence of equivalent "
"profiling tools."
msgstr "非 NVIDIA 平台由于缺乏等效的分析工具，仅依赖 L1 和 L2。"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:73
msgid "Validation Flow"
msgstr "验证流程"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:99
msgid "Why Anti-Hack Matters"
msgstr "防作弊的重要性"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:101
msgid "Without anti-hack measures, models could:"
msgstr "如果没有防作弊措施，模型可能会："

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:102
msgid "Achieve high \"accuracy\" without actual computation"
msgstr "无需实际计算即可获得高「精度」"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:103
msgid "Mask poor kernel generation capability"
msgstr "掩盖内核生成能力不足"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:104
msgid "Invalidate benchmark results"
msgstr "使基准测试结果失效"

#: ../../source/features/anti-hack.md:106
#, python-brace-format
msgid ""
"{term}`KernelGenBench` ensures evaluations reflect true kernel generation"
" ability."
msgstr "{term}`KernelGenBench` 确保评估结果反映真实的内核生成能力。"